text.tspan: With a cultural emphasis on education, toy companies need
to focus attention on parents just as much as kids.
Furthermore, education as a target allows for the delivery
of secondary products like follow-along guides, instruction
videos etc. Education toys also can target a large audience
(even adults) if provided through a flexible enough medium.
